<div id="connect-tab" class="tab-content">
  <div class="connect-form">
    <h2>🔐 Connect Store via OAuth</h2>
    <p>Connect a store using OAuth. The app will automatically use the store's dedicated app credentials if configured.</p>
    <form action="/install" method="GET" style="margin-top:20px;">
      <label>Store URL:</label>
      <input 
        type="text" 
        name="shop" 
        id="connectShopUrl"
        placeholder="your-store.myshopify.com" 
        required
        oninput="checkAppConfig()"
      />
      <small style="display:block; margin-bottom:15px; color:#666;">
        Format: your-store.myshopify.com
      </small>
      
      <div id="appStatusMessage"></div>
      
      <button type="submit">🔗 Connect Store via OAuth</button>
    </form>
  </div>
  
  <div class="manual-setup">
    <h3>💡 Can't use OAuth? Try Manual Setup</h3>
    <p>If you're a collaborator or having OAuth issues, use the "Manual Setup" tab for an alternative method.</p>
  </div>
</div>
